oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Ronnie Reno Recording Session - 1980-03-22 - Tape 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recording is of a variety of Ronnie Reno (musician) studio recordings. The recordings were produced by Wayne Carson. The tape was created on March 22, 1980 at the LSI Sound Studio Inc. The tape is one of an unknown number of tapes from the recording session.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Ronnie Reno
